'''Robert DeWayne Papenbrook''' ([[1955]] - [[2006]]) was an American voice actor. He voiced [[Gimli]], [[Théoden]] and unnamed [[Uruk-hai|Uruks]] in the video game ''[[The Lord of the Rings: War of the Ring]]''.
